data.description: Welcome to the sought after neighborhood of Blue Creek Farms! Sitting just under an acre, situated on a stunning cul-de-sac lot with mature trees and so much space...404 Blue Moon Ct is exactly what you have been waiting for. Enjoy FOUR bedrooms and a gorgeous open concept living, dining, and kitchen layout with many updated features throughout. Do not miss the stunning owners suite bathroom updates! Enjoy the fully fenced backyard with its very own fire-pit area, perfect for entertaining! The home is equipped with a soft water system and a full home security system that will convey. Blue Creek Farms is located a short drive to both New River Air Station and North Topsail Beach. This beauty is a must see - schedule your showing today!
